      "range": "6898-6919",
      "markText": "名牌上写着两个人的名字：圆城寺苍，立花茜。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6898&rangeEnd=6919",
