    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_23_5548-5568",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5548-5568",
      "markText": "叠在我最喜欢的、阿布四四方方的大拇指上。",
      "totalCount": 242,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5548&rangeEnd=5568",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5548&rangeEnd=5568"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_23_5408-5424",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5408-5424",
      "markText": "“我知道阿玲的生命力有多高洁。”",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5408&rangeEnd=5424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5408&rangeEnd=5424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_6_5072-5100",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5072-5100",
      "markText": "这是一段标记好终点的关系，就像一场知道何时会结束的电影。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5072&rangeEnd=5100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5072&rangeEnd=5100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_7_2447-2506",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2447-2506",
      "markText": "“我希望到时候，我不是为自己的苍老而悲伤，而是为逝去的年华而自豪；不是叹息从前真好，而是为匣子里那个年轻的我而骄傲。”",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2447&rangeEnd=2506",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2447&rangeEnd=2506"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_24_11570-11601",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "11570-11601",
      "markText": "杂货店的老板名叫由里，是阿玲在墨尔本留学期间打工时认识的前辈。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=11570&rangeEnd=11601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=11570&rangeEnd=11601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_18_2240-2327",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2240-2327",
      "markText": "“而且，您猜拳老是输给别人，彩票期期都买却从没中过奖，乘列车基本轮不上座位，总是抽走公司纸巾盒里的最后一张纸巾，别人都能用上新的。网上购物，有时还会买到质量差到吓人的残品。”",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2240&rangeEnd=2327",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2240&rangeEnd=2327"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_6_5582-5601",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5582-5601",
      "markText": "动笔前的脑海中的作品，才是完美的作品。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5582&rangeEnd=5601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5582&rangeEnd=5601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_6_3925-3938",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3925-3938",
      "markText": "一切只要开始就必将会结束。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3925&rangeEnd=3938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3925&rangeEnd=3938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_4_3770-3793",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3770-3793",
      "markText": "不知道阿布记不记得，那一天我穿的也是这件罩衫。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_22_6199-6258",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "6199-6258",
      "markText": "“我当然是在尽兴生活啦，但我啊，还觉得人生是有很多次的，无论从哪里、以怎样的方式，都可以重新开始。我更喜欢这样去想。”",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6199&rangeEnd=6258",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6199&rangeEnd=6258"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_4_533-567",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "533-567",
      "markText": "就像锅中煮开的水的泡沫会咕嘟咕嘟地消失一样，到处都充满了开始和结束。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=533&rangeEnd=567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=533&rangeEnd=567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_5_2278-2340",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2278-2340",
      "markText": "刚才他也是这样说的，我想。他对那个女孩说，方便的时候联系他。这就是阿布的态度，把选择权交给对方。而他一定不会拒绝对方的邀约。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098439&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2340",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ea322e0813ab8cf3g019fcc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2340"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098439_7_2622-2672",
